I do not clamed to own any of the images, some I found as are and some i put together myself (mostly by croping album art and moving things around and upscaling)
List of posters so far:
Albums
1.1989 *Made it myself
2. Fearless TV (from the vault) *Crop and moved text around
3. Fearless *Crop and slight fill
4. Fearless TV *Found online with slight tweaks
5 Lover *Crop and moved text around
6. Midnights *Found online with slight tweaks
7. Red TV *Made it myself
8. Red *Made it myself
9. Speak Now TV *Found online with slight tweaks
10. Speak Now *Found online with slight tweaks
11.Taylor Swift *Crop and moved text around
Lives:
1. 1989 World Tour *Found online with slight tweaks
2. Betty Live from the 2020 ACMA *Crop and moved text around
3. Reputation Stadium Tour *Found online with slight tweaks
4. Speak Now Live *Found online with slight tweaks
5. The Eras Tour *Found online with slight tweaks
Other
1. Poster from the movie Amsterdam *Found online with slight tweaks
2. Poster from the music video "I bet you think about me" *Found online with slight tweaks
3. Lavender Haze *tweaked album art
4. Lover Photoshoot Photo
5. Now *Found online with slight tweaks
6. READ *Found online with slight tweaks
7. willow (90's mix) *tweaked album art
